Unit test
=========

pip install: #Running tests with Tox
    tox

By default:
tox -l
py3
flake8
docs
isort

# Running older versions
tox -e py35-postgres -- --settings=my_postgres_settings

# Js version
tox -e javascript

# Only run some of the tests
# For example, if youâ€™d like to run tests only for generic relations and internationalization.
./runtests.py --settings=path.to.settings generic_relations i18n

# Running selenium tests
./runtests.py --selenium=firefox,chrome

Run everything:
# You need these for the tests
argon2-cffi 16.1.0+
bcrypt
docutils
geoip2
jinja2 2.7+
numpy
Pillow
PyYAML
pytz (required)
setuptools
memcached, plus a supported Python binding
gettext (gettext on Windows)
selenium
sqlparse (required)